Lagos-based communication and events consultancy, AT3 Resources is set to mark its fifth year of operations by hosting a week-long digital marketing boot camp for Small and Medium Scale Enterprises (SMEs), themed: ‘Leveraging Possibilities for SMEs in The Digital Age.’  The digital marketing boot camp will enable SMEs to take advantage of growth prospects in the digital media era. The boot camp will include a deep dive into areas like, online reputation management, communications strategy, digital marketing, brand & visuals, and the ‘Always on’ Entrepreneur. 